<h1><span id="Staunton_Gambit">Staunton Gambit</span></h1>
<h3><span id="2._e4">2. e4</span></h3>
<p>The type of approach one might expect to be successful against the Dutch in view of the weak h5-e8 diagonal. Practice has shown that Black has adequate resources and it difficult for white to show much after a skirmish to recover the pawn sacrifice.
</p>
<p><b>1.d4 f5 2.e4</b>
